comments.text:
here’s how I would turn 200,000 Chase points into an $11,758 luxury trip to Paris ✈️✨ 

I swear I'm going to teach you guys how to go to luxury places for not luxury prices!!! 


✈️ NYC → Paris Business Class (@AirFrance)  Transfer 60,000 @Chase points to Air France (@flyingBlue) if you don’t know how to transfer points, check out my other videos! Book that $8,194 seat for 60k points

🏨 3 Nights at Hotel du Louvre (@Hyatt)  Transfer 105,000 Chase points to World of Hyatt (≈ 35,000 points per night at this 5-star Paris hotel)

🥂 Book a table to Le Girafe (if you have the @chasesapphire, you can book it through experiences or call Sapphire Concierge) 

✈️ Fly home Paris → NYC  Transfer 18,750 points to Air France for economy (Or upgrade back if you have extra points 😉)

💰 Total cash value of this trip: $11,758  💳 Value if you redeemed 200k points for cash: ~$2,000

Comment any questions! What card/points amount should I do next?
